Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the shore already\Nso that I can knock you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me!\NI'll shut you up right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Cartwheel, Iron Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slam you into the corner of\Nthe tower using this momentum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It indeed looks like\NI'll get smashed into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chapa!\N--I've got both your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't move around at will in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! Even if you do that,\Nyou can't stop this momentum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not totally true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,70 mm 0.2 Cola Cannon!\NA bit of Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! The momentum has died down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rotation stopped! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is enough!\NWe're already above the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,70 mm 1.5 Max Cola Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up already, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Don't tell me\Nhe broke the fridge door...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a little fatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much stuff in that fridge did you eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Sogeking. Don't lose your posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get me a lawyer! I'll sue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try this out first, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This is a dream! This is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, come already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys sure do some weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Hey! Are you really gonna do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the demon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... Stars are coming out of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tiger? Tiger?\NI'm in trouble! I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hit me good. Stars are\Ncoming out of my nose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be unreasonable!\NAre you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to fight us seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it seems like we have no\Nchoice but to play rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll cut off the hand of the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Like I said, don't you\Nhave any better ideas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for stupid arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up, nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just give it up, nose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Please hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uncontrollable! Chopper's Forbidden Rumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone with\Nso little self-discipline as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he gained weight in the\Nfew minutes I took my eyes off of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't... need to be...\Nneed to be... need to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not concerned! Just speak normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "need to be concerned," right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I was... I was... I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, so you can cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's no need\Nto be concerned, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... I was... That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just look! Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Digest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! What?! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Digest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Digest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing! How does that work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand years at sea, and a\Nthousand years in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathing in the wind and drinking dewdrops,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trained myself, living as a hermit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, I've... I've... I've...\NI've acquired this "Life Return"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially, if you extend\Nyour consciousness everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from your hair to your internal organs,\Ntoes, even the tip of your downy hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no part of your body\Nthat you can't manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extending your consciousness\Neven to the tip of your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read about that kind\Nof ability in a book before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called something like biofeedback...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your hair moves around like\Nan octopus because of that ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoyoi! An octopus?! How terribly rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me... a valiant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lion... will... will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it matter which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get caught by that, it'll be all over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol! Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that stick doesn't\Neven have a pointed tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q! Q! Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Gong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, he won't budge unless\NI attack with Arm Point or Horn Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rumble balls are potent drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One in six hours is a proper dosage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take more than that,\Nit'll be a huge strain on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that... the second one will\Nalter the transformation wavelength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so it'll be hard to\Ncontrol my transformations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the third one, I'll lose consciousness\Nand hardly be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? I can take just\None more and get strengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll roast you on a skewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishi Kabob!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoi! Yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do anything, I'm just wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is high-risk, but it'll give me a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yoyoi!\N--This is all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll somehow settle this within three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Horn Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabob!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi! Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was afraid, I can't control\Nmy transformations. Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could somehow use Arm Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could give him a cloven\Nattack with all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is dangerous with the fire spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for me to be stuck\Nwith a guy with no key on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry up and get the #2 key...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and free Zoro and Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or we can't rescue Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting in order to save our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a tough animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hair changed into the shape of hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it! I can't be\Ndefeated in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm their only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishi Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showing mercy is never... part of a lion's fury!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the second rumble ball is like gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are seven transformations in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the probability of\Ngetting Arm Point is one in seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could get it, I could hammer\Nmy strongest attack into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishi Kabob!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my friends... Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong one! Why doesn't it come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is at the end of its rope.\NI somehow have to get Arm Point out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoyoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yoyoi!\N--Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's out! I didn't notice it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put everything I have\Ninto this... into this attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cloven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishi Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I back off now, I won't get another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cloven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body! Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Roseo Metel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my best attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Splendid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was indeed a beautiful blizzard of...\Ncherry blossom petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you hell! Yoyoyoi yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick! Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it... I no longer have\Nenergy left to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what in the world did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't remember" doesn't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good that no one died, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you were sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire country was making\Na big fuss about that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to settle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I did something that terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost destroyed an entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine that you love experiments,\Njust like your old man did,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for something like that, you have\Nto do it only after thorough planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thorough planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were not doing it for\Nfun at all. I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly why you\Nneed to be even more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctors are always\Nentrusted with people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small mistakes can become irreversible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always walking on\Nthe edge of a cliff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even imagine what kind of result
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,careless actions can cause, then you\Nshould give up on becoming a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you inherited\Neverything from that quack,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including his predisposition for causing a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world always has its\Ntroublesome seeds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Doctorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never do it again,\Nso please don't kick me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a fool. Hurry up and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I can't even go out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, it'll be a disgrace to your manhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an evening in a mountain\Nvillage where you can hear the cicadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a journey to hell\Nthat you knew could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leaves I broke off of a willow tree\Nbranch to give to you as a parting gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hoping for your return someday,\Nare colored crimson!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it! Now, now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson... Song of Willow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... That's right. I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He slipped away from my Hair Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Doctorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Doctor put his life on the\Nline in order to save the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to put my life on the\Nline in order to save my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna die anyway, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please, nobody come into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used three Rumble Balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I lost consciousness and after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that your Devil Fruit\Npowers went out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever go down that path, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an excessive power that destroys\Nfoes, friends, and even your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you turned into was just like a real...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Big news! Big news! Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the big news today, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to appear again after a long while!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Buggy guy and his men will go\Nwild noisily, messily, tiredly, disorderly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now... Why don't you\Neat and calm yourself down? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Ahh! Anyway, this is big news, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.87,0:23:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Boss Luffy Returns! Is it a Dream\Nor Reality? Lottery Ruckus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a policeman!!
